2014年3月11日，菲律宾政府向中国驻马尼拉临时代办提交外交抗议，指责[[中国海警|中国海警]]在3月9日阻止菲律宾两艘民用船只向坐滩仁爱礁的马德雷山号军舰提供人员换防和物资补给<ref>''Inquirer'' - "Philippines protests Ayungin Shoal incident".[http://globalnation.inquirer.net/100173/dfa-issues-protest-on-chinas-expulsion-of-ph-ships-2] {{Wayback|url=http://globalnation.inquirer.net/100173/dfa-issues-protest-on-chinas-expulsion-of-ph-ships-2 |date=20200809211708 }} - accessed 13 March 2014.</ref>。这是中国第一次阻止菲律宾对马德雷山号进行补给。3月13日，菲律宾利用小型飞机对驻守马德雷山号的海军陆战队员进行了空中补给<ref>''Channel News Asia'' - "Philippines drops food to troops after China 'blockade'",{{cite web |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/philippines-drops-food-to/1033960.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313182424/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/philippines-drops-food-to/1033960.html |archivedate=2014-03-13 }} - accessed 13 March 2014.</ref>。2014年4月1日，菲律宾冲破中国海警和民用船只封锁，再次对马德雷山号提供人员换防和物资补给，并邀请外国记者随船同行<ref>''China Times'' - "Philippine sailors gloat as China fails to block Sierra Madre supply run" {{cite web |url=http://www.wantchinatimes.com/news-subclass-cnt.aspx?id=20140401000062&cid=1101 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-04-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407130608/http://www.wantchinatimes.com/news-subclass-cnt.aspx?id=20140401000062&cid=1101 |archivedate=2014-04-07 }}.</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://globalnation.inquirer.net/103076/afp-uses-couriers-to-foil-china-spies |title=AFP uses couriers to foil China spies |last1=Dizon |first1=Nikko |date=29 April 2014 |website=globalnation.inquirer.net |publisher=Philippine Daily Inquirer |accessdate=29 April 2014 |archive-date=2020-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223185731/https://globalnation.inquirer.net/103076/afp-uses-couriers-to-foil-china-spies |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年9月，菲律宾为遭到中国海警围困的11名驻守该舰的海军陆战队员空投了补给物资，英国广播公司记者{{link-en |鲁伯特·温费尔德-海伊斯|Rupert Wingfield-Hayes}}登上马德雷山号采访，马德雷山号此时已经被严重腐蚀破败不堪，船侧布满大小孔洞，海浪可以轻易飞溅进入船舱，随时有解体的危险<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/special/2014/newsspec_8701/index.html|title=China's Island Factory|work=BBC News|date=9 September 2014|accessdate=January 26, 2015|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219070127/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/special/2014/newsspec_8701/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年7月，菲律宾海军发言人埃德加多·阿雷法罗中校（Colonel Edgardo Arevalo）说，他们正在加固马德雷山号，以保证舰上最基本的生存条件<ref>{{cite web|last1=Agence France-Presse|title=PH repairs crumbling South China Sea ship outpost|url=http://globalnation.inquirer.net/126107/ph-repairs-crumbling-south-china-sea-ship-outpost|publisher=Inquirer|accessdate=4 May 2016|date=15 July 2015|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206081046/https://globalnation.inquirer.net/126107/ph-repairs-crumbling-south-china-sea-ship-outpost|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

